available(uint256).notice: Check if a name is available for registration

multicall(bytes[]).notice: Execute multiple calls in a single transaction

nameExpires(uint256).notice: Get the expiry time of a name

reclaim(uint256,address).notice: Reclaim ownership of a name in the registry

registerWithConfig(uint256,address,uint2.notice: Register a name with resolver configuration

renew(uint256,uint256).notice: Renew a name by extending its registration period

setResolver(address).notice: Set the resolver for the TLD

tokenURI(uint256).notice: Returns the token URI for a given token ID
